Ayyadsoft Web
This is a professional software to help Tutors at catch up on the tasks given to students at university.
The software is a place as well for new ideas coming up from strategic mind students.
The software is a place for educational chat and submitting the tasks given at university which also includes all the tools needed to help the student graduate and be more succesful while studying.
the software also includes videos a place for chat between the tutor and the students as well as tasks made by past students.
it is a type of communication but only for educational services.

Requirements 
IPADS
WIFI
communication daily between the tutor and students
the hometasks has to be completed
nerw ideas from students about the fields they study at university for example if they are studying engineering new ideas like how to develop cheaper electric vehicles.
